2026-06-17  Arc 6 item 14.4: undo/redo broadcast the kind-appropriate message (Tasks.reversal_broadcast) — {:task_updated} for value edits, {:task_moved} for move/reorder, structural {:task_created}/{:task_deleted} for create/delete by direction — instead of a blanket {:task_created}; and the performer patches just the row for value edits rather than a full load_tree. Cost proportional to the change, for everyone.
